Adu, the only player to score hat-tricks in the Under-17 World Championships and at an Under-20 World Cup, played with Altidore at youth level, and even set up both of his goals in a 2-1 win against Brazil at the Under-20 World Cup in 2007.

Despite his clear promise, Adu has never lived up to the hype that saw him labelled 'the next Pele', and though he has been capped 17 times for USA his club career has since him travel between continents in search of regular football.

